sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Bot as Existing AI Bot
    participant Conn as Bot Connector API
    participant Engine as Workflow Engine
    participant MCP as MCP Servers
    participant LLM as LLM Service
    
    User->>Bot: Check violations for account 12345
    Bot->>Conn: POST /api/v1/connector/trigger
    Note over Conn: Authenticate and Validate
    
    Conn->>LLM: Parse Intent and Entities
    LLM-->>Conn: intent check_violations account 12345
    
    Conn->>Engine: Start Workflow Execution
    Engine->>MCP: Execute DB2 Query
    MCP-->>Engine: Violation Data
    Engine->>MCP: Execute SQL Server Query
    MCP-->>Engine: Additional Data
    
    Engine->>LLM: Generate Summary
    LLM-->>Engine: Natural Language Summary
    
    Engine-->>Conn: Execution Result
    
    alt Synchronous Response
        Conn-->>Bot: 200 OK with Result
        Bot-->>User: Display Result Card
    else Async with Callback
        Conn-->>Bot: 202 Accepted with execution_id
        Conn->>Bot: POST callback_url with Result
        Bot-->>User: Display Result Card
    end
